OL,3,CHit-and-run drug driver pleads guilty
OL,4,Cto leaving boy to die on road
OL,6,FThe mother of a seven-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdied in a hit and run in Kent says she
OL,8,Fforgives the man who left him to die
OL,9,Fin the road.JWilliam Brown was
OL,10,Fretrieving his football from the coast
OL,11,Froad at Sandgate on 6 December 2023,
OL,12,Fwhen he was struck by a van driven by
OL,13,FStewart Powell. William died at the
OL,14,Fscene.
OL,16,FPowell, 49, pleaded guilty to leaving
OL,17,Fthe scene of a collision at Folkestone
OL,18,FMagistrates' Court on Friday 24 May.
