OL,6,FThe court heard that Powell's van
OL,7,Fstruck William, who was then hit by a
OL,8,Fsecond vehicle.
OL,10,FThe prosecutor contrasted the actions
OL,11,Fof the two drivers.
OL,13,FThe woman driving the second vehicle
OL,14,Fstopped, dialled 999 and stayed with
OL,15,FWilliam.
OL,17,FPowell left the scene and did not
OL,18,Freport the accident until the next
OL,19,Fday, telling police the incident had
OL,20,F"stressed him out".
