OL,3,CHit-and-run drug driver pleads guilty
OL,4,Cto leaving boy to die on road
OL,6,FLaura Brown, William's mother, said:
OL,7,F"I would say to Stewart, we forgive
OL,8,Fyou. I think you made some really poor
OL,9,Fchoices, pre and post the death of
OL,10,FWilliam.
OL,12,F"We feel sad for you. You know, he has
OL,13,Fto live with that as well. He didn't
OL,14,Fset out to kill William that day,
OL,15,Fthat's one thing for sure, but he just
OL,16,Fmade some awful choices and I believe
OL,17,Fthat he wishes he could change back
OL,18,Ftime and so do we.
