OL,6,F"But if he could come on board and do
OL,7,Fa drug drive campaign, I think it
OL,8,Fcould be so impactful and so powerful
OL,9,Fif it came from Stewart himself and
OL,10,Ftogether we could make a change."
OL,12,FPowell, from Dunstall Gardens, St
OL,13,FMary's Bay, admitted leaving the scene
OL,14,Fof a collision and driving without
OL,15,Finsurance.
OL,17,FPowell will be sentenced in July but
OL,18,Fthe court imposed an immediate driving
OL,19,Fban.
